# Capacitor native shells — Vercel only ships the Next.js app + /api/v1/*.
# The iOS/Android projects are bundled into the App Store / Play Store
# binary via `npx cap sync` on a developer machine, not via Vercel.
/ios
/android

# Static export output — Vercel uses the default `next build`, not
# `build:static`. The `out/` dir is only consumed by Capacitor.
/out

# Capacitor + iOS toolchain caches that should never reach Vercel.
**/Pods
**/.gradle
**/DerivedData
